'''''Psilocybe kumaenorum''''' is a species of mushroom in the family [[Strophariaceae]].<ref name="Guzman 1998"/> The mushroom contains the medicinal compound [[psilocybin]]. It is in the section ''Zapotecorum'' of the genus ''[[Psilocybe]]'', other members of this section include ''[[Psilocybe muliercula]]'', ''[[Psilocybe angustipleurocystidiata]]'', ''[[Psilocybe aucklandii]]'', ''[[Psilocybe collybioides]]'', ''[[Psilocybe graveolens]]'', ''[[Psilocybe zapotecorum]]'', ''[[Psilocybe pintonii]]'', ''[[Psilocybe subcaerulipes]]'', ''[[Psilocybe moseri]]'', ''[[Psilocybe zapotecoantillarum]]'', ''[[Psilocybe zapotecocaribaea]]'', and ''[[Psilocybe antioquiensis]]''.<ref name="Guzman2012">{{cite journal |last=Guzmán |first=Gastón |authorlink=Gastón Guzmán |title= New Taxonomical and Ethnomycological Observations on Psilocybe S.S. From Mexico, Africa and Spain |journal=Acta Botanica Mexicana |year=2012 |volume=100 |pages=79–106 |url=http://dialnet.unirioja.es/descarga/articulo/3988750.pdf}}</ref><ref name="Ramirez-Cruz2013">{{cite journal |last1=Ramírez-Cruz |first1=Virginia |last2=Guzmán |first2=Gastón |last3= Villalobos-Arámbula |first3=Alma Rosa |last4=Rodríguez |first4=Aarón |last5=Matheny |first5=Brandon |last6= Sánchez-García |first6=Marisol |last7=Guzmán-Dávalos |first7=Laura |title=Phylogenetic inference and trait evolution of the psychedelic mushroom genus ''Psilocybe'' sensu lato (Agaricales)|journal=Botany |year=2013 |volume=91 |pages=573–591 |url=http://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/abs/10.1139/cjb-2013-0070#.VH_zGTHF9Vs |doi=10.1139/cjb-2013-0070}}</ref>
